<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 06:21:21 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>联合国 COP16 谈判中世界在 2030 年自然目标方面落后</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/world-lags-2030-nature-goals-headed-into-un-cop16-talks-2024-10-21/</link><description>世界将在 2022 年达成有史以来最雄心勃勃的协议，以在十年结束时制止对自然的破坏。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 06:03:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/world-lags-2030-nature-goals-headed-into-un-cop16-talks-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>据彭博社报道，大都会人寿正在洽谈以 10 亿至 15 亿美元收购 PineBridge 在中国以外的资产</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/metlife-talks-buy-pinebridges-ex-china-assets-1-bln-15-bln-bloomberg-news-2024-10-21/</link><description>据彭博社周一报道，总部位于纽约的大都会人寿保险公司正在就收购 PineBridge Investments 在中国境外的资产进行深入谈判，交易价值可能为 10 亿至 15 亿美元。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 06:02:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/metlife-talks-buy-pinebridges-ex-china-assets-1-bln-15-bln-bloomberg-news-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>由于中国销量下降，Forvia 第三季度销量略有下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/car-parts-supplier-forvia-posts-slightly-lower-q3-sales-2024-10-21/</link><description>按收入计算，全球第七大汽车零部件供应商 Forvia 周一报告称，第三季度销售额与去年同期相比略有下降。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 05:45:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/car-parts-supplier-forvia-posts-slightly-lower-q3-sales-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>香港当局称土壤感染导致猴子死亡，第11例死亡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-authorities-say-soil-infection-killed-monkeys-11th-dies-2024-10-21/</link><description>当局表示，类鼻疽是一种细菌感染，导致香港动物园至少 9 只猴子死亡，周末又有两只猴子死亡，过去一周猴子总数达到 11 只。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 02:39:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-authorities-say-soil-infection-killed-monkeys-11th-dies-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市波动，比特币和黄金上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-10-21/</link><description>周一，在香港股市疲软的压力下，亚洲股市上下波动，但随着“特朗普交易”的持续增加，比特币触及三个月高点。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 02:33:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国上市公司争相利用央行资金购买股票</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-listed-companies-rush-tap-central-bank-funding-share-purchases-2024-10-21/</link><description>根据交易所备案文件，在中国人民银行启动 420 亿美元融资计划几天后，已有 20 多家中国上市公司宣布计划利用央行特别贷款购买股票。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 01:27:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-listed-companies-rush-tap-central-bank-funding-share-purchases-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>可可的美国队将在联合杯小组赛中迎战加拿大队</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/cocos-us-team-face-canada-united-cup-group-stage-2024-10-21/</link><description>头号种子美国队将在小组赛中对阵邻国加拿大队，届时可可·高夫将在下赛季初于悉尼和珀斯举行的第三届联合杯混合团体锦标赛中首次亮相。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 01:26:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/cocos-us-team-face-canada-united-cup-group-stage-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国下调主要贷款利率以支持增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-cuts-benchmark-loan-prime-rates-by-25-bps-2024-10-21/</link><description>作为振兴经济一揽子刺激措施的一部分，上个月降低了其他政策利率，中国周一按照预期在月度定价中下调了基准贷款利率。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 01:12:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-cuts-benchmark-loan-prime-rates-by-25-bps-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>军演结束一周后，美国和加拿大海军驶​​过台湾海峡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-canadian-navies-sail-through-taiwan-strait-week-after-war-games-2024-10-20/</link><description>周日，一艘美国和一艘加拿大军舰一起驶过敏感的台湾海峡，距离中国在台湾进行新一轮军演不到一周，北京谴责这次任务具有“破坏性”。</description><pubDate>Sun, 20 Oct 2024 23:11:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-canadian-navies-sail-through-taiwan-strait-week-after-war-games-2024-10-20/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：中国降息迫在眉睫，美国蓬勃发展</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-10-20/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Sun, 20 Oct 2024 21:50:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-10-20/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体称，中国加强了对两用物品的出口管制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-boosts-export-controls-dual-use-items-state-media-says-2024-10-19/</link><description>官方通讯社新华社周六称，中国总理李强已签署国务院令，公布所谓两用物项出口管制条例，该条例将于 2024 年 12 月 1 日生效。</description><pubDate>Sat, 19 Oct 2024 11:50:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-boosts-export-controls-dual-use-items-state-media-says-2024-10-19/</guid></item><item><title>英国外交大臣承诺与中国关系保持“一致性”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk-foreign-secretary-pledges-consistency-relations-with-china-2024-10-19/</link><description>英国外交大臣戴维·拉米(David Lammy)周六表示，随着伦敦寻求在新工党政府领导下重置与北京的关系，企业希望与中国的贸易保持“稳定和明确”。</description><pubDate>Sat, 19 Oct 2024 08:14:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk-foreign-secretary-pledges-consistency-relations-with-china-2024-10-19/</guid></item><item><title>中国习近平敦促导弹部队增强威慑和作战能力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-xi-urges-missile-troops-boost-deterrence-combat-capabilities-2024-10-19/</link><description>中国官方媒体周六报道称，国家主席习近平周四视察了中国人民解放军火箭军的一个旅，敦促部队增强“威慑和作战能力”。</description><pubDate>Sat, 19 Oct 2024 08:02:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-xi-urges-missile-troops-boost-deterrence-combat-capabilities-2024-10-19/</guid></item><item><title>无人机制造商大疆就中国军方名单起诉五角大楼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/chinese-dronemaker-dji-sues-pentagon-over-chinese-military-listing-2024-10-19/</link><description>全球最大的无人机制造商表示，这一指定对其造成了财务损失。</description><pubDate>Sat, 19 Oct 2024 00:15:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/chinese-dronemaker-dji-sues-pentagon-over-chinese-military-listing-2024-10-19/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普称如果中国进入台湾他将对中国征收关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/trump-says-he-would-impose-tariffs-china-if-china-went-into-taiwan-2024-10-18/</link><description>据《华尔街日报》报道，共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普表示，如果中国“进入台湾”，他将对中国征收额外关税。</description><pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 22:43:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/trump-says-he-would-impose-tariffs-china-if-china-went-into-taiwan-2024-10-18/</guid></item></channel></rss>